title: Rune King
description: Lord of the Runes Manhua At first he was just another one of those unqualified to be a rune bearer, but thanks to a “system” that completely changed his destiny, he was able to become one of the great commanders of the War Zone, where he led humanity to counterattack the great army of rune beasts.
